data.description: This delightful North Salt Lake gem features 3-bedrooms, 2.5-bathrooms with a townhome style layout is found in the Foxboro Coventry development, known to be a highly desirable location in a quiet neighborhood. The front door is within a walking distance of the neighborhood park which makes it great for taking the kids for a quick visit to the park. Easy commute to the I- 215 freeway makes getting around town a breeze. The interior welcomes you with stylish lighting, remarkable ceilings, and a fireplace. Stylish kitchen is bright with natural light and attractive U-shaped layout. More than merely serene, the highly functional master bedroom includes a walk-in closet, sitting space, and private bath with tub and shower. The other two bedrooms are situated above the ground floor for privacy are rich with ample closet space and ready for your decorative touch. Attached one-car garage. Exteriors include refreshing pool and club house with gym and lounge. You're going to feel great waking up here every morning. Schedule your showing today!
